title: Dell 14 Premium Review: Creator Laptop That's Rock Solid to a Fault
description: Dell's top consumer laptop isn't without its charms, but it's simply too heavy for its size.
content: Dell must equate "premium" with sturdiness and heft. That's the only reason I can think of as to why the Dell 14 Premium is one of the hardiest and heaviest 14-inch laptops I've ever encountered. On … [+12278 chars]
